Notes: Amanda Nechuta becomes UWSP's all-time leading scorer and now ranks seventh
in WIAC history with 1666 points...UWSP opened up 19-8 lead nine minutes into
game...UWSP led by at least 10 points throughout second half...UWSP scored all
13 first half field goals in the paint...UWSP's 10th straight victory.
Game.Officials: Jack Blume,  Blaine Hilgendorf,  Phil Streit
